{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 1321, "title": "Handle VP8 decoding errors to avoid stopping the decoding thread", "body": "When we switched to using PyAV for VP8 encoding, we stopped handling the case where decoding a package fails. This causes the decoding thread to stop, breaking video reception. Apply the same logic we use for H.264 decoding : if we are unable to decode a package, log a warning and return an empty list of frames.\r\n\r\nFixes: #1315", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "f96d88c9c8a804c8981c933b96e5762818ea29fb", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "aiortc/aiortc"}, "url": "https://github.com/aiortc/aiortc/pull/1321", "createdAt": "2025-05-24T08:23:55Z", "mergedAt": "2025-05-24T08:27:39Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "aiortc/aiortc"}, "sha": "f96d88c9c8a804c8981c933b96e5762818ea29fb"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/aiortc/aiortc/pull/1321.diff", "number": 1321, "created_at": "2025-05-24T08:23:55Z", "merged_at": "2025-05-24T08:27:39Z", "resolved_issues": [1315]}
{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 1334, "title": "only update remote description if it exists", "body": "while technically calling addIceCandidate before setRemoteDescription should not be allowed this can (and has) worked prior to #1318\r\n\r\nFixes #1332", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "c3f6b41b3e654204e032cf2e77b1a11a5f308042", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "aiortc/aiortc"}, "url": "https://github.com/aiortc/aiortc/pull/1334", "createdAt": "2025-06-03T14:33:30Z", "mergedAt": "2025-10-13T07:14:31Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "aiortc/aiortc"}, "sha": "c3f6b41b3e654204e032cf2e77b1a11a5f308042"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/aiortc/aiortc/pull/1334.diff", "number": 1334, "created_at": "2025-06-03T14:33:30Z", "merged_at": "2025-10-13T07:14:31Z", "resolved_issues": [1332]}
